VALUES ('8e7f148c-145c-4811-af3d-90094d5eb7ad', 'The student wants to emphasize the most empirically supported approach documented in the notes. Which choice most effectively synthesizes relevant information to accomplish this goal?', '• Turbine prototype 5001 employs tubercle-inspired blade geometry modeled on humpback whale fins
